{
  "stem": "27507.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And I don't think many people had a good-- had any very hopeful feeling about what was-- I think there were people who were deluding themselves, for sure, and people who thought it was quite inconceivable that the end was going to be death.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "But I think there was a general people tried to avoid being deported as much as they could.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "What happened then was the ghetto get already on the beginning of the action, ghetto was immediately surrounded by Polish police, and even more by German auxiliary battalions of Ukrainians, and of the Lats, and of the Lithuanians.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And those Lithuanians, and Lats, and Ukrainians, together with the SS of course, and the Jewish police, they were then responsible for getting people to the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And they did it in the way that they were closing areas of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "They were closing blocks of houses, or streets, or part of the street, and telling everybody to come down, and then taking them, with few exceptions, to the [GERMAN], and putting them on the trains.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And it was all done with a tremendous amount of-- particularly then in this summer-- with a tremendous amount of brutality, in the most brutal and horrible way, which was all purpose done, because the idea was, I suppose, that if one terrorizes the people enough, then nobody is going to be able to offer any resistance, or even to refuse, or even to run away.",
      "word_count": 66
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And it worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "It worked in so far--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sorry?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I think when I come to my particular experience, maybe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But already then, in summer, the brutality was just amazing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- brutality was simply by-- first of all, everything was going to-- was doing with screaming and shouting.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was never any normal talking.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
